Privacy policy
BACtrack Privacy Policy
Last Updated: December 5, 2024
This privacy policy sets out how KHN Solutions LLC ("KHN"), doing business as BACtrack ("BACtrack"), uses and protects any information that you give BACtrack when you visit our website ("Website") or purchase and use our products, connected hardware products, software, mobile applications and services (collectively "the Products and Services"). This includes the BACtrack breathalyzers and accessories, BACtrack and BACtrack View mobile applications, and BACtrack View services. Your continued use of our website, software or Products and Services indicates your agreement to these policies.
BACtrack.com is not intended for use by minors under 16 and we do not knowingly collect personal information from persons under the age of 16. BACtrack's Products and Services are not intended for use by minors under 18 and we do not knowingly market our Products and Services to persons under the age of 18.
1. Information We Collect
In the course of using our Website, Products and Services, you may provide, and we may collect certain personal information, including:
Categories of Personal Information
Types of Personal Information
Sources of Personal Information
